<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_403" id="200v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_403_r2l1">Mıcheln Ʒollner </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_403_r2l2"><expan>Vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt beuor . Mıchel ʒollner / als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_403_r2l3">etc / das haben wır <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Alſo wenn Jr ın den <expan>nehſt<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_403_r2l4">viij <expan>tag<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu vns meynt ʒu <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> . ſo ſüllt Jr ʒu vnd von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_403_r2l5">vns für vns vnd dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on <expan>geu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> ʒwen tag geleyt <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_403_r2l6">ſo wellen wır eẅr rede <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hören / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> poſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_403_r2l7"><expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nıca<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>Jnuocau<ex>i</ex><hi rend="sup">t</hi></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_403" id="200v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Micheln Zollner</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Uns<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst bevor. Michel Zollner, als ir uns
                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt etc., das haben wir
                <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Also wenn ir in den
              <expan>nehst<ex>en</ex></expan> viii <expan>tag<ex>en</ex></expan> zu uns meynt zu
                <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>, so süllt ir zu und von uns für uns und die
                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan> zwen tag geleyt
                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, so wellen wir ewr rede <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
            hören. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi> post
                <expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>invocav<ex>i</ex><hi rend="sup">t</hi></expan>.</ab>
</div>
